<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196938>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Sangkulirang Peninsula, Kalimantan Timur, Borneo, showing location of Sungai (river) Marang, in Bengalon drainage (above) and collecting sites of Nemacheilus marang in Sungai Marang (below). 1, Tepian Langsat village (type locality); 2, mouth of Sungai Marang; and 3, Sungai Jelai." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196938/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

